article.description: — Angelo Allegri had 17 points as UNC Greensboro topped Chattanooga 74-66 on Saturday.
article.headline: Allegri carries UNC Greensboro over Chattanooga 74-66
article.linkText: Allegri carries UNC Greensboro over Chattanooga 74-66
article.story: CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -- — Angelo Allegri had 17 points as UNC Greensboro topped Chattanooga 74-66 on Saturday. Jarrett Hensley had 12 points for UNC Greensboro (10-5, 5-2 Southern Conference), which earned its fourth straight win. Kaleb Hunter added 10 points and seven rebounds. Isaiah Miller had six rebounds. Darius Banks had 18 points for the Mocs (12-5, 3-5). David Jean-Baptiste added 13 points. Malachi Smith had 12 points and six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
